{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775836544166,"sessionID":"ses_287e60928ffeqArVIHjn8RDz06","part":{"id":"prt_d781b38d9001xk42OljzExOze0","messageID":"msg_d781b3179001BVG1C6JVlSFB5C","sessionID":"ses_287e60928ffeqArVIHjn8RDz06","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"call_bd740f9e373f4dd596ce0657","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/delta-spec.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/delta-spec.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # AR-013: Redis 存储实现 — Delta Spec\n2: \n3: ## Context\n4: \n5: - **Module:** `pkg/store`\n6: - **Language:** Go\n7: - **Size:** M\n8: - **Base specs:** `session-store/spec.md`, `session-store/design.md`, `deployment/client-go.md`\n9: \n10: ## Delta Requirements\n11: \n12: ### Requirement: Redis client initialization\n13: The Redis implementation SHALL construct a `redisv9.Client` using `REDIS_ADDR` and `REDIS_PASSWORD` environment variables. The system SHALL require `REDIS_ADDR` to be non-empty. The system SHALL require non-empty `REDIS_PASSWORD` unless `REDIS_PASSWORD_REQUIRED` is set case-insensitively to `\"false\"`.\n14: \n15: #### Scenario: Successful initialization with address and password\n16: - **GIVEN** `REDIS_ADDR` is set to `\"localhost:6379\"` and `REDIS_PASSWORD` is set to `\"secret\"`\n17: - **WHEN** the Redis store initializes\n18: - **THEN** a `redisv9.Client` is constructed with `Addr: \"localhost:6379\"` and `Password: \"secret\"`\n19: - **AND** no error is returned\n20: \n21: #### Scenario: Missing address fails\n22: - **GIVEN** `REDIS_ADDR` is empty or unset\n23: - **WHEN** the Redis store initializes\n24: - **THEN** initialization returns an error indicating `REDIS_ADDR` is required\n25: \n26: #### Scenario: Password required by default\n27: - **GIVEN** `REDIS_ADDR` is set, `REDIS_PASSWORD` is empty, and `REDIS_PASSWORD_REQUIRED` is unset\n28: - **WHEN** the Redis store initializes\n29: - **THEN** initialization fails with an error stating password is required\n30: \n31: #### Scenario: Password bypass when explicitly disabled\n32: - **GIVEN** `REDIS_ADDR` is set, `REDIS_PASSWORD` is empty, and `REDIS_PASSWORD_REQUIRED` is set to `\"false\"` (case-insensitive)\n33: - **WHEN** the Redis store initializes\n34: - **THEN** a `redisv9.Client` is constructed with empty password\n35: - **AND** no error is returned\n36: \n37: #### Scenario: Password not required when flag is not false\n38: - **GIVEN** `REDIS_ADDR` is set, `REDIS_PASSWORD` is empty, and `REDIS_PASSWORD_REQUIRED` is set to `\"true\"`\n39: - **WHEN** the Redis store initializes\n40: - **THEN** initialization fails with an error stating password is required\n41: \n42: ### Requirement: Redis connection options\n43: The system SHALL build `redisv9.Options` with `Addr` from `REDIS_ADDR` and `Password` from `REDIS_PASSWORD`.\n44: \n45: #### Scenario: Options construction\n46: - **GIVEN** `REDIS_ADDR=\"redis-host:6380\"` and `REDIS_PASSWORD=\"pass123\"`\n47: - **WHEN** `makeRedisOptions()` is called\n48: - **THEN** the returned options have `Addr: \"redis-host:6380\"` and `Password: \"pass123\"`\n49: \n50: ### Requirement: Redis StoreSandbox pipeline\n51: The Redis implementation SHALL execute `StoreSandbox` as a pipeline of three commands: `SETNX` on the session key with JSON value, `ZADD` on `session:expiry` with score = `ExpiresAt.Unix()`, and `ZADD` on `session:last_activity` with score = `time.Now().Unix()`. The system SHALL fail if any command in the pipeline returns an error.\n52: \n53: #### Scenario: Successful store pipeline\n54: - **GIVEN** a valid `SandboxInfo` with non-zero `ExpiresAt` and session id `s1`\n55: - **WHEN** `StoreSandbox(ctx, sandbox)` is called on the Redis store\n56: - **THEN** the pipeline executes `SETNX session:s1 <json>`, `ZADD session:expiry <expires_unix> s1`, `ZADD session:last_activity <now_unix> s1` and returns nil\n57: \n58: #### Scenario: Pipeline error propagation\n59: - **GIVEN** the Redis server is unreachable during `StoreSandbox`\n60: - **WHEN** the pipeline executes\n61: - **THEN** the method returns a non-nil error and no partial state is committed\n62: \n63: #### Scenario: Nil sandbox rejected\n64: - **GIVEN** `StoreSandbox(ctx, nil)` is called\n65: - **WHEN** the method executes\n66: - **THEN** an error is returned indicating sandbox is nil\n67: - **AND** no Redis commands are issued\n68: \n69: #### Scenario: Zero ExpiresAt rejected\n70: - **GIVEN** `SandboxInfo` has `ExpiresAt == time.Time{}`\n71: - **WHEN** `StoreSandbox(ctx, sandbox)` is called\n72: - **THEN** an error is returned indicating ExpiresAt is required\n73: - **AND** no Redis commands are issued\n74: \n75: ### Requirement: Redis UpdateSandbox XX semantics\n76: The Redis implementation SHALL use `SET key value XX` for `UpdateSandbox`. If the key does not exist, the system SHALL return an error indicating the key does not exist.\n77: \n78: #### Scenario: Update existing key\n79: - **GIVEN** session key `session:s1` exists\n80: - **WHEN** `UpdateSandbox(ctx, sandbox)` is called\n81: - **THEN** the JSON value is overwritten and the method returns nil\n82: \n83: #### Scenario: Update missing key\n84: - **GIVEN** session key `session:s1` does not exist\n85: - **WHEN** `UpdateSandbox(ctx, sandbox)` is called\n86: - **THEN** the method returns an error containing `key not exists`\n87: \n88: #### Scenario: Nil sandbox rejected on update\n89: - **GIVEN** `UpdateSandbox(ctx, nil)` is called\n90: - **WHEN** the method executes\n91: - **THEN** an error is returned indicating sandbox is nil\n92: \n93: ### Requirement: Redis DeleteSandboxBySessionID pipeline\n94: The Redis implementation SHALL execute `DeleteSandboxBySessionID` as a pipeline of three commands: `DEL` on the session key, `ZREM` on `session:expiry`, and `ZREM` on `session:last_activity`.\n95: \n96: #### Scenario: Full deletion\n97: - **GIVEN** session `s1` exists with entries in both ZSETs\n98: - **WHEN** `DeleteSandboxBySessionID(ctx, \"s1\")` succeeds\n99: - **THEN** `GET session:s1` returns nil and both ZSETs no longer contain member `s1`\n100: \n101: #### Scenario: Delete non-existent session\n102: - **GIVEN** session `ghost` does not exist\n103: - **WHEN** `DeleteSandboxBySessionID(ctx, \"ghost\")` is called\n104: - **THEN** the pipeline executes (DEL returns 0, ZREM returns 0) and no error is returned\n105: \n106: ### Requirement: Redis GetSandboxBySessionID\n107: The Redis implementation SHALL retrieve a sandbox document using `GET session:{id}`. If the key does not exist, the system SHALL return `ErrNotFound`.\n108: \n109: #### Scenario: Existing session retrieved\n110: - **GIVEN** a sandbox document exists at key `session:s1`\n111: - **WHEN** `GetSandboxBySessionID(ctx, \"s1\")` is called\n112: - **THEN** the JSON value is unmarshaled to `*types.SandboxInfo` and returned with nil error\n113: \n114: #### Scenario: Missing session returns ErrNotFound\n115: - **GIVEN** no key exists at `session:missing`\n116: - **WHEN** `GetSandboxBySessionID(ctx, \"missing\")` is called\n117: - **THEN** the method returns `ErrNotFound`\n118: \n119: ### Requirement: Redis ListExpiredSandboxes query\n120: The Redis implementation SHALL query `session:expiry` using `ZRANGEBYSCORE` with range `-inf` to `before.Unix()` and `LIMIT 0 limit`. When `limit <= 0`, the method SHALL return `nil, nil`.\n121: \n122: #### Scenario: List with limit zero\n123: - **GIVEN** expired sessions exist in the index\n124: - **WHEN** `ListExpiredSandboxes(ctx, before, 0)` is called\n125: - **THEN** the method returns `nil, nil` without querying Redis\n126: \n127: #### Scenario: List with positive limit\n128: - **GIVEN** three sessions have expiry scores ≤ `before.Unix()`\n129: - **WHEN** `ListExpiredSandboxes(ctx, before, 2)` is called\n130: - **THEN** at most two `SandboxInfo` pointers are returned\n131: \n132: #### Scenario: List with negative limit\n133: - **GIVEN** expired sessions exist\n134: - **WHEN** `ListExpiredSandboxes(ctx, before, -1)` is called\n135: - **THEN** the method returns `nil, nil`\n136: \n137: ### Requirement: Redis ListInactiveSandboxes query\n138: The Redis implementation SHALL query `session:last_activity` using `ZRANGEBYSCORE` with range `-inf` to `before.Unix()` and `LIMIT 0 limit`. When `limit <= 0`, the method SHALL return `nil, nil`.\n139: \n140: #### Scenario: Inactive list with negative limit\n141: - **GIVEN** inactive sessions exist\n142: - **WHEN** `ListInactiveSandboxes(ctx, before, -1)` is called\n143: - **THEN** the method returns `nil, nil`\n144: \n145: #### Scenario: Inactive list with positive limit\n146: - **GIVEN** two sessions have last-activity scores ≤ `before.Unix()`\n147: - **WHEN** `ListInactiveSandboxes(ctx, before, 5)` is called\n148: - **THEN** up to two `SandboxInfo` pointers are returned\n149: \n150: ### Requirement: Redis UpdateSessionLastActivity precondition\n151: The Redis implementation SHALL verify the session key exists via `GET` before executing `ZADD` on `session:last_activity`. If the key is absent, the method SHALL return `ErrNotFound`. If `at` is zero time, the system SHALL use `time.Now()`.\n152: \n153: #### Scenario: Activity update with zero time\n154: - **GIVEN** session `s1` exists and `at` is `time.Time{}`\n155: - **WHEN** `UpdateSessionLastActivity(ctx, \"s1\", at)` is called\n156: - **THEN** `ZADD session:last_activity <now_unix> s1` is executed\n157: \n158: #### Scenario: Activity update for missing session\n159: - **GIVEN** session `s1` does not exist\n160: - **WHEN** `UpdateSessionLastActivity(ctx, \"s1\", now)` is called\n161: - **THEN** the method returns `ErrNotFound`\n162: \n163: #### Scenario: Empty session ID rejected\n164: - **GIVEN** empty session ID `\"\"`\n165: - **WHEN** `UpdateSessionLastActivity(ctx, \"\", at)` is called\n166: - **THEN** an error is returned indicating session ID is empty\n167: \n168: ### Requirement: Redis pipeline GET orphan tolerance\n169: The Redis implementation SHALL handle nil results from pipeline `GET` commands when loading sandboxes by session IDs. Entries with nil results SHALL be skipped without failing the batch.\n170: \n171: #### Scenario: Redis orphan ZSET member\n172: - **GIVEN** session id `ghost` is in `session:last_activity` but `session:ghost` does not exist\n173: - **WHEN** `ListInactiveSandboxes` loads the batch via pipeline GETs\n174: - **THEN** `ghost` is omitted from the result slice\n175: - **AND** no error is raised\n176: \n177: ### Requirement: Redis Ping response validation\n178: The Redis implementation SHALL issue `PING` and validate the response equals `PONG`.\n179: \n180: #### Scenario: Healthy Redis\n181: - **GIVEN** Redis server is running\n182: - **WHEN** `Ping(ctx)` is called\n183: - **THEN** the response is `PONG` and nil error is returned\n184: \n185: #### Scenario: Unreachable Redis\n186: - **GIVEN** Redis server is down\n187: - **WHEN** `Ping(ctx)` is called\n188: - **THEN** an error is returned indicating connection failure\n189: \n190: ### Requirement: Redis Close operation\n191: The Redis implementation SHALL close the client connection via `cli.Close()`.\n192: \n193: #### Scenario: Client closed successfully\n194: - **GIVEN** an active Redis store\n195: - **WHEN** `Close()` is called\n196: - **THEN** `cli.Close()` is invoked and nil is returned\n197: \n198: ### Requirement: Redis fixed key patterns\n199: The Redis implementation SHALL use the following fixed key patterns: `sessionPrefix = \"session:\"`, `expiryIndexKey = \"session:expiry\"`, `lastActivityIndexKey = \"session:last_activity\"`.\n200: \n201: #### Scenario: Session key construction\n202: - **GIVEN** session id `abc`\n203: - **WHEN** the store constructs the key\n204: - **THEN** the key is `session:abc`\n205: \n206: ### Requirement: Redis ZSET score semantics\n207: The system SHALL use Unix seconds as scores in sorted sets. Expiry index score = `float64(ExpiresAt.Unix())`. Last activity score = `float64(time.Now().Unix())` on store, `float64(at.Unix())` on update.\n208: \n209: #### Scenario: Expiry score is sandbox ExpiresAt\n210: - **GIVEN** a sandbox with `ExpiresAt` set to a specific time T\n211: - **WHEN** `StoreSandbox` adds to `session:expiry`\n212: - **THEN** the score is `float64(T.Unix())`\n213: \n214: #### Scenario: Last activity score is current time on store\n215: - **GIVEN** `StoreSandbox` is called at time T\n216: - **WHEN** the sandbox is added to `session:last_activity`\n217: - **THEN** the score is `float64(T.Unix())`\n218: \n219: ### Requirement: Provider selection via STORE_TYPE\n220: When `STORE_TYPE` is unset or empty, the system SHALL default to `redis` (case-insensitive comparison). Supported values are `redis` and `valkey`; any other value SHALL fail initialization.\n221: \n222: #### Scenario: Unset STORE_TYPE defaults to redis\n223: - **GIVEN** `STORE_TYPE` environment variable is not set\n224: - **WHEN** `Storage()` initializes\n225: - **THEN** the Redis implementation is constructed\n226: \n227: #### Scenario: Invalid STORE_TYPE\n228: - **GIVEN** `STORE_TYPE=memcached`\n229: - **WHEN** `Storage()` initializes\n230: - **THEN** initialization fails with an unsupported store type error\n231: \n232: ### Requirement: Singleton initialization\n233: The system SHALL use `sync.Once` to ensure `initStore` executes exactly once. `Storage()` SHALL call `initStoreOnce.Do(initStore)` and on error SHALL call `klog.Fatalf(\"init store failed: %v\", err)`.\n234: \n235: #### Scenario: Concurrent Storage calls\n236: - **GIVEN** ten goroutines call `Storage()` simultaneously\n237: - **WHEN** all calls complete\n238: - **THEN** `initStore` has executed exactly once and all goroutines receive the same `Store` instance\n239: \n240: #### Scenario: Failed initialization is fatal\n241: - **GIVEN** required environment variables are missing\n242: - **WHEN** `Storage()` is called\n243: - **THEN** `klog.Fatalf` is invoked with message `\"init store failed: %v\"`\n244: - **AND** the process terminates\n\n(End of file - total 244 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-013: Redis 存储实现 — Delta Spec\n\n## Context\n\n- **Module:** `pkg/store`\n- **Language:** Go\n- **Size:** M\n- **Base specs:** `session-store/spec.md`, `session-store/design.md`, `deployment/client-go.md`\n\n## Delta Requirements\n\n### Requirement: Redis client initialization\nThe Redis implementation SHALL construct a `redisv9.Client` using `REDIS_ADDR` and `REDIS_PASSWORD` environment variables. The system SHALL require `REDIS_ADDR` to be non-empty. The system SHALL require non-empty `REDIS_PASSWORD` unless `REDIS_PASSWORD_REQUIRED` is set case-insensitively to `\"false\"`.\n\n#### Scenario: Successful initialization with address and password\n- **GIVEN** `REDIS_ADDR` is set to `\"localhost:6379\"` and `REDIS_PASSWORD` is set to `\"secret\"`\n- **WHEN** the Redis store initializes\n- **THEN** a `redisv9.Client` is constructed with `Addr: \"localhost:6379\"` and `Password: \"secret\"`\n- **AND** no error is returned\n","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/delta-spec.md","time":{"start":1775836544158,"end":1775836544165}}}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775836545540,"sessionID":"ses_287e60928ffeqArVIHjn8RDz06","part":{"id":"prt_d781b3d7700131PfiLsiR4qTx7","messageID":"msg_d781b3179001BVG1C6JVlSFB5C","sessionID":"ses_287e60928ffeqArVIHjn8RDz06","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"call_87e03a13def74c7a9d944227","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-011/delta-spec.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-011/delta-spec.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # AR-011: Router JWT 认证与签发 — Delta Spec\n2: \n3: ## Purpose\n4: \n5: 为 `pkg/router` 模块实现完整的 JWT  inbound 认证与 outbound 签发能力。当前 `/v1` 下的所有调用路由完全无保护，任何客户端均可直接调用沙箱。本变更在现有 `JWTManager`（仅支持 outbound RS256 签名）基础上，新增 inbound token 验证、`AuthMiddleware` gin 中间件，并将中间件注册到 `/v1` 路由组，同时保持 `/health/*` 端点公开可访问。本变更是 AR-009（HTTP 反向代理核心）的安全增强，满足 TDD 清单中 `Test-RT-1`（无效 JWT → 401）和 `Test-RT-2`（过期 JWT → Token Expired）的要求。\n6: \n7: ## Requirements\n8: \n9: ### Requirement: JWTManager 新增 PublicKey 访问器\n10: \n11: The system SHALL 在 `pkg/router/jwt.go` 的 `JWTManager` 结构体上新增 `PublicKey()` 方法，返回内部持有的 RSA 公钥，供 inbound token 验证使用。\n12: \n13: ```go\n14: func (m *JWTManager) PublicKey() *rsa.PublicKey\n15: ```\n16: \n17: 该方法 SHALL 为纯读取操作，不修改内部状态，线程安全。\n18: \n19: #### Scenario: 返回有效公钥\n20: \n21: - **GIVEN** `JWTManager` 已通过 `NewJWTManager()` 初始化\n22: - **WHEN** `PublicKey()` 被调用\n23: - **THEN** 返回非 nil 的 `*rsa.PublicKey`，且与生成密钥对时的公钥一致\n24: \n25: #### Scenario: 多次调用返回同一公钥\n26: \n27: - **GIVEN** `JWTManager` 已初始化\n28: - **WHEN** `PublicKey()` 被连续调用多次\n29: - **THEN** 每次返回的指针地址相同\n30: \n31: ---\n32: \n33: ### Requirement: JWTManager 新增 ParseAndValidateToken 方法\n34: \n35: The system SHALL 在 `JWTManager` 上新增 `ParseAndValidateToken(tokenString string) (jwt.MapClaims, error)` 方法，用于验证 inbound JWT token。\n36: \n37: 验证规则 SHALL 满足：\n38: 1. 使用 RS256 签名算法，以内部 RSA 公钥验证签名\n39: 2. 必须校验 `exp`（过期时间）claim，过期 token 返回明确错误\n40: 3. 必须校验 `iat`（签发时间）claim\n41: 4. 必须校验 `iss`（签发者）claim，期望值为 `\"agentcube-router\"`\n42: 5. 设置 1 分钟 leeway（宽容窗口），容忍时钟偏差\n43: 6. 拒绝非 RS256 算法的 token（如 HS256、RS512 等）\n44: \n45: 错误区分：\n46: - 签名无效 → 返回包含 `\"invalid signature\"` 语义的错误\n47: - Token 过期 → 返回包含 `\"token is expired\"` 语义的错误\n48: - 签发者不匹配 → 返回包含 `\"invalid issuer\"` 语义的错误\n49: - 格式错误（非 JWT 字符串）→ 返回包含 `\"invalid token\"` 语义的错误\n50: \n51: #### Scenario: 有效 token 解析成功\n52: \n53: - **GIVEN** 使用同一 `JWTManager` 的 `GenerateToken` 签发的未过期 token\n54: - **WHEN** `ParseAndValidateToken(tokenString)` 被调用\n55: - **THEN** 返回 `jwt.MapClaims`，包含 `iss: \"agentcube-router\"`、`exp`、`iat` 及自定义 claims\n56: - **AND** error 为 nil\n57: \n58: #### Scenario: 过期 token 被拒绝\n59: \n60: - **GIVEN** 一个 `exp` 为过去时间的 token（使用相同密钥签发）\n61: - **WHEN** `ParseAndValidateToken(tokenString)` 被调用\n62: - **THEN** 返回错误，错误信息包含 `\"token is expired\"`\n63: \n64: #### Scenario: 伪造签名被拒绝\n65: \n66: - **GIVEN** 使用不同 RSA 密钥对签发的 token\n67: - **WHEN** `ParseAndValidateToken(tokenString)` 被调用\n68: - **THEN** 返回错误，错误信息包含 `\"invalid signature\"`\n69: \n70: #### Scenario: 非 RS256 算法被拒绝\n71: \n72: - **GIVEN** 使用 HS256 算法签发的 token\n73: - **WHEN** `ParseAndValidateToken(tokenString)` 被调用\n74: - **THEN** 返回错误，错误信息包含 `\"unexpected signing method\"` 或类似描述\n75: \n76: #### Scenario: 签发者不匹配被拒绝\n77: \n78: - **GIVEN** 使用相同密钥但 `iss` 为 `\"other-service\"` 的 token\n79: - **WHEN** `ParseAndValidateToken(tokenString)` 被调用\n80: - **THEN** 返回错误，错误信息包含 `\"invalid issuer\"`\n81: \n82: #### Scenario: 畸形 token 被拒绝\n83: \n84: - **GIVEN** 输入字符串为 `\"not-a-jwt-token\"`\n85: - **WHEN** `ParseAndValidateToken(tokenString)` 被调用\n86: - **THEN** 返回错误，错误信息包含 `\"invalid token\"`\n87: \n88: #### Scenario: 空字符串被拒绝\n89: \n90: - **GIVEN** 输入字符串为空 `\"\"`\n91: - **WHEN** `ParseAndValidateToken(tokenString)` 被调用\n92: - **THEN** 返回错误\n93: \n94: #### Scenario: Leeway 容忍时钟偏差\n95: \n96: - **GIVEN** token 的 `exp` 为 30 秒前，leeway 为 1 分钟\n97: - **WHEN** `ParseAndValidateToken(tokenString)` 被调用\n98: - **THEN** token 被视为有效，解析成功\n99: \n100: ---\n101: \n102: ### Requirement: AuthMiddleware 中间件\n103: \n104: The system SHALL 在 `pkg/router/middleware.go` 中新增 `AuthMiddleware(jwtManager *JWTManager) gin.HandlerFunc`，实现基于 JWT Bearer token 的 HTTP 认证。\n105: \n106: 中间件行为：\n107: 1. 从请求 `Authorization` header 提取 token\n108: 2. 验证 header 格式为 `Bearer <token>`\n109: 3. 调用 `jwtManager.ParseAndValidateToken(token)` 验证 token\n110: 4. 验证通过：将解析后的 claims 存入 `c.Set(\"claims\", claims)`，调用 `c.Next()`\n111: 5. 验证失败：根据错误类型返回对应 HTTP 响应并 `c.Abort()`\n112: \n113: 错误响应格式：\n114: \n115: | 错误类型 | HTTP 状态码 | Response Body |\n116: |----------|------------|---------------|\n117: | 缺少 Authorization header | 401 | `{\"error\": \"missing authorization header\", \"code\": \"UNAUTHORIZED\"}` |\n118: | Authorization 格式错误（非 Bearer） | 401 | `{\"error\": \"invalid authorization format\", \"code\": \"UNAUTHORIZED\"}` |\n119: | Token 过期 | 401 | `{\"error\": \"token is expired\", \"code\": \"TOKEN_EXPIRED\"}` |\n120: | Token 签名无效 | 401 | `{\"error\": \"invalid token\", \"code\": \"UNAUTHORIZED\"}` |\n121: | Token 解析其他错误 | 401 | `{\"error\": \"invalid token\", \"code\": \"UNAUTHORIZED\"}` |\n122: \n123: #### Scenario: 有效 Bearer token 通过认证\n124: \n125: - **GIVEN** 请求携带 `Authorization: Bearer <valid-jwt>`，token 由当前 JWTManager 签发且未过期\n126: - **WHEN** `AuthMiddleware` 处理该请求\n127: - **THEN** `c.Next()` 被调用，请求继续传递到下游 handler\n128: - **AND** `c.Get(\"claims\")` 返回解析后的 `jwt.MapClaims`\n129: \n130: #### Scenario: 缺少 Authorization header 返回 401\n131: \n132: - **GIVEN** 请求无 `Authorization` header\n133: - **WHEN** `AuthMiddleware` 处理该请求\n134: - **THEN** 响应 401，body 为 `{\"error\": \"missing authorization header\", \"code\": \"UNAUTHORIZED\"}`\n135: - **AND** `c.Abort()` 被调用\n136: \n137: #### Scenario: 非 Bearer 格式返回 401\n138: \n139: - **GIVEN** 请求携带 `Authorization: Basic dXNlcjpwYXNz`\n140: - **WHEN** `AuthMiddleware` 处理该请求\n141: - **THEN** 响应 401，body 为 `{\"error\": \"invalid authorization format\", \"code\": \"UNAUTHORIZED\"}`\n142: - **AND** `c.Abort()` 被调用\n143: \n144: #### Scenario: Bearer 后无 token 返回 401\n145: \n146: - **GIVEN** 请求携带 `Authorization: Bearer `（token 部分为空）\n147: - **WHEN** `AuthMiddleware` 处理该请求\n148: - **THEN** 响应 401，body 为 `{\"error\": \"invalid authorization format\", \"code\": \"UNAUTHORIZED\"}`\n149: - **AND** `c.Abort()` 被调用\n150: \n151: #### Scenario: 过期 token 返回 TOKEN_EXPIRED\n152: \n153: - **GIVEN** 请求携带 `Authorization: Bearer <expired-jwt>`\n154: - **WHEN** `AuthMiddleware` 处理该请求\n155: - **THEN** 响应 401，body 为 `{\"error\": \"token is expired\", \"code\": \"TOKEN_EXPIRED\"}`\n156: - **AND** `c.Abort()` 被调用\n157: \n158: #### Scenario: 伪造 token 返回 UNAUTHORIZED\n159: \n160: - **GIVEN** 请求携带 `Authorization: Bearer <forged-jwt>`（使用不同密钥签名）\n161: - **WHEN** `AuthMiddleware` 处理该请求\n162: - **THEN** 响应 401，body 为 `{\"error\": \"invalid token\", \"code\": \"UNAUTHORIZED\"}`\n163: - **AND** `c.Abort()` 被调用\n164: \n165: #### Scenario: 自定义 claims 传递到下游\n166: \n167: - **GIVEN** Token 包含自定义 claim `\"session_id\": \"sess-001\"`\n168: - **WHEN** 认证通过，下游 handler 执行\n169: - **THEN** handler 可通过 `c.Get(\"claims\")` 获取 claims，其中 `session_id` 为 `\"sess-001\"`\n170: \n171: ---\n172: \n173: ### Requirement: /v1 路由组注册 AuthMiddleware\n174: \n175: The system SHALL 在 `pkg/router/server.go` 的 `registerRoutes()` 方法中，将 `AuthMiddleware` 注册到 `/v1` 路由组的中间件栈中。\n176: \n177: 中间件注册顺序 SHALL 为：\n178: 1. `gin.Logger()`\n179: 2. `gin.Recovery()`\n180: 3. `AuthMiddleware(s.jwtManager)`（新增）\n181: 4. `ConcurrencyLimitMiddleware(s.config.MaxConcurrentRequests)`\n182: \n183: `AuthMiddleware` SHALL 位于 `gin.Recovery()` 之后、`ConcurrencyLimitMiddleware` 之前，确保：\n184: - panic 恢复在认证之前（避免认证逻辑 panic 导致 500）\n185: - 未认证请求不消耗并发配额（在 `ConcurrencyLimitMiddleware` 之前拦截）\n186: \n187: #### Scenario: /v1 路由组携带 AuthMiddleware\n188: \n189: - **GIVEN** `NewServer` 构造完成\n190: - **WHEN** 检查 `/v1` 路由组的中间件栈\n191: - **THEN** 中间件按顺序包含：Logger、Recovery、AuthMiddleware、ConcurrencyLimit\n192: \n193: #### Scenario: 未认证请求被拦截在并发限制之前\n194: \n195: - **GIVEN** 并发配额已满（1000 个请求正在处理）\n196: - **WHEN** 无 Authorization header 的请求到达 `/v1/...`\n197: - **THEN** 响应 401 `UNAUTHORIZED`，不被 429 拒绝\n198: \n199: ---\n200: \n201: ### Requirement: /health 端点保持公开\n202: \n203: The system SHALL 确保 `/health/live` 和 `/health/ready` 端点不受 `AuthMiddleware` 保护，K8s liveness/readiness probe 无需携带 JWT token 即可访问。\n204: \n205: 当前实现中 health 端点已在 `/v1` 组之外注册（`s.engine.GET(\"/health/live\", ...)`），本变更 SHALL 保持此结构不变。\n206: \n207: #### Scenario: 健康检查无需认证\n208: \n209: - **GIVEN** 无 `Authorization` header 的请求\n210: - **WHEN** `GET /health/live` 被调用\n211: - **THEN** 响应 200，body 包含 `{\"status\": \"ok\"}`\n212: \n213: #### Scenario: 就绪检查无需认证\n214: \n215: - **GIVEN** 无 `Authorization` header 的请求\n216: - **WHEN** `GET /health/ready` 被调用\n217: - **THEN** 响应 200 或 503（取决于组件就绪状态），不被 401 拦截\n218: \n219: ---\n220: \n221: ### Requirement: outbound JWT 签发保持不变\n222: \n223: The system SHALL 保持现有 outbound JWT 签发行为不变：在 `proxy.go` 的 `forwardToSandbox` 中，当入口点 kind 为 `Sandbox` 或 `SandboxClaimKind` 时，使用 `jwtManager.GenerateToken` 生成 JWT 并注入到 `Authorization: Bearer <token>` header 中转发至沙箱。\n224: \n225: 本变更不修改 outbound 签发逻辑，仅新增 inbound 验证能力。\n226: \n227: #### Scenario: Sandbox 请求携带 outbound JWT\n228: \n229: - **GIVEN** 代理请求转发到 kind 为 `Sandbox` 的入口点\n230: - **WHEN** `forwardToSandbox` 执行\n231: - **THEN** 出站请求携带 `Authorization: Bearer <jwt>`，其中 jwt 由 `jwtManager.GenerateToken` 签发\n232: \n233: #### Scenario: CodeInterpreter 请求不携带 outbound JWT\n234: \n235: - **GIVEN** 代理请求转发到 kind 为 `CodeInterpreter` 的入口点\n236: - **WHEN** `forwardToSandbox` 执行\n237: - **THEN** 出站请求不携带 `Authorization` header（保持现有行为）\n238: \n239: ---\n240: \n241: ### Requirement: JWT 配置可扩展\n242: \n243: The system SHALL 在 `pkg/router/config.go` 中扩展 `Config` 结构体，新增以下 JWT 相关配置字段：\n244: \n245: | 字段 | 类型 | 默认值 | 说明 |\n246: |------|------|--------|------|\n247: | `JWTExpiration time.Duration` | `time.Duration` | `5 * time.Minute` | JWT token 有效期 |\n248: | `JWTIssuer string` | `string` | `\"agentcube-router\"` | JWT iss claim |\n249: | `JWTLeeway time.Duration` | `time.Duration` | `1 * time.Minute` | 验证宽容窗口 |\n250: \n251: `NewDefaultConfig()` SHALL 为新增字段设置默认值。\n252: \n253: #### Scenario: 默认 JWT 配置\n254: \n255: - **GIVEN** 未传入 JWT 相关 CLI 标志\n256: - **WHEN** `NewDefaultConfig()` 被调用\n257: - **THEN** `JWTExpiration = 5m`，`JWTIssuer = \"agentcube-router\"`，`JWTLeeway = 1m`\n258: \n259: #### Scenario: 自定义 JWT 过期时间\n260: \n261: - **GIVEN** Config 中 `JWTExpiration = 10 * time.Minute`\n262: - **WHEN** `JWTManager.GenerateToken` 被调用\n263: - **THEN** 生成的 token `exp` claim 为当前时间 + 10 分钟\n264: \n265: ---\n266: \n267: ### Requirement: JWTManager 支持配置注入\n268: \n269: The system SHALL 修改 `NewJWTManager()` 构造函数，支持接收可选的配置参数：\n270: \n271: ```go\n272: type JWTConfig struct {\n273:     Expiration time.Duration\n274:     Issuer     string\n275:     Leeway     time.Duration\n276: }\n277: \n278: func NewJWTManager(config *JWTConfig) (*JWTManager, error)\n279: ```\n280: \n281: 当 `config` 为 nil 时，使用默认值（Expiration=5m, Issuer=\"agentcube-router\", Leeway=1m）。\n282: \n283: `GenerateToken` SHALL 使用 `JWTConfig.Expiration` 和 `JWTConfig.Issuer` 设置 token 的 `exp` 和 `iss` claims。\n284: \n285: `ParseAndValidateToken` SHALL 使用内部 RSA 公钥和 `JWTConfig.Leeway` 进行验证。\n286: \n287: #### Scenario: nil 配置使用默认值\n288: \n289: - **GIVEN** `NewJWTManager(nil)` 被调用\n290: - **WHEN** JWTManager 构造完成\n291: - **THEN** 内部配置为 Expiration=5m, Issuer=\"agentcube-router\", Leeway=1m\n292: \n293: #### Scenario: 自定义配置生效\n294: \n295: - **GIVEN** `NewJWTManager(&JWTConfig{Expiration: 10*time.Minute, Issuer: \"custom-issuer\", Leeway: 2*time.Minute})`\n296: - **WHEN** 生成并验证 token\n297: - **THEN** token 的 `exp` 为当前时间 + 10 分钟，`iss` 为 `\"custom-issuer\"`，验证 leeway 为 2 分钟\n298: \n299: ---\n300: \n301: ### Requirement: 编译与测试门禁\n302: \n303: The system SHALL 满足以下门禁：\n304: 1. `go build ./pkg/router/...` 编译通过\n305: 2. `go test ./pkg/router/... -v` 全部通过\n306: 3. `go test -race ./pkg/router/...` 无 data race 告警\n307: 4. 每个 `*.go` 文件有对应的 `*_test.go` 文件\n308: 5. T/C 比率 > 0.4\n309: 6. 无 `log.Printf` 残留（使用 `slog` 或 `klog`）\n310: \n311: #### Scenario: pkg/router 编译通过\n312: \n313: - **GIVEN** 所有 router 代码已编写完成\n314: - **WHEN** `go build ./pkg/router/...` 执行\n315: - **THEN** 无编译错误\n316: \n317: #### Scenario: 无效 JWT 返回 401（Test-RT-1）\n318: \n319: - **GIVEN** 请求携带无效 JWT（伪造签名）\n320: - **WHEN** 请求到达 `/v1` 路由\n321: - **THEN** 响应 401 Unauthorized\n322: \n323: #### Scenario: 过期 JWT 返回 Token Expired（Test-RT-2）\n324: \n325: - **GIVEN** 请求携带已过期的 JWT\n326: - **WHEN** 请求到达 `/v1` 路由\n327: - **THEN** 响应 401，body 包含 `\"token is expired\"` 或 `\"TOKEN_EXPIRED\"`\n328: \n329: #### Scenario: Race detector 无告警\n330: \n331: - **GIVEN** 并发场景测试已覆盖（AuthMiddleware 并发请求、JWTManager 并发签发与验证）\n332: - **WHEN** `go test -race ./pkg/router/...` 执行\n333: - **THEN** 无 data race 告警\n334: \n335: #### Scenario: jwt.go 有对应测试文件\n336: \n337: - **GIVEN** `pkg/router/jwt.go` 已修改\n338: - **WHEN** 检查 `pkg/router/jwt_test.go` 是否存在\n339: - **THEN** 文件存在且包含对 `PublicKey()` 和 `ParseAndValidateToken()` 的测试\n340: \n341: #### Scenario: middleware.go 有对应测试文件\n342: \n343: - **GIVEN** `pkg/router/middleware.go` 已修改\n344: - **WHEN** 检查 `pkg/router/middleware_test.go` 是否存在\n345: - **THEN** 文件存在且包含对 `AuthMiddleware` 的测试\n\n(End of file - total 345 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-011: Router JWT 认证与签发 — Delta Spec\n\n## Purpose\n\n为 `pkg/router` 模块实现完整的 JWT  inbound 认证与 outbound 签发能力。当前 `/v1` 下的所有调用路由完全无保护，任何客户端均可直接调用沙箱。本变更在现有 `JWTManager`（仅支持 outbound RS256 签名）基础上，新增 inbound token 验证、`AuthMiddleware` gin 中间件，并将中间件注册到 `/v1` 路由组，同时保持 `/health/*` 端点公开可访问。本变更是 AR-009（HTTP 反向代理核心）的安全增强，满足 TDD 清单中 `Test-RT-1`（无效 JWT → 401）和 `Test-RT-2`（过期 JWT → Token Expired）的要求。\n\n## Requirements\n\n### Requirement: JWTManager 新增 PublicKey 访问器\n\nThe system SHALL 在 `pkg/router/jwt.go` 的 `JWTManager` 结构体上新增 `PublicKey()` 方法，返回内部持有的 RSA 公钥，供 inbound token 验证使用。\n\n```go\nfunc (m *JWTManager) PublicKey() *rsa.PublicKey\n```\n\n该方法 SHALL 为纯读取操作，不修改内部状态，线程安全。\n\n#### Scenario: 返回有效公钥\n","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-011/delta-spec.md","time":{"start":1775836545529,"end":1775836545537}}}}
{"type":"step_finish","timestamp":1775836545628,"sessionID":"ses_287e60928ffeqArVIHjn8RDz06","part":{"id":"prt_d781b424d00101F5rAynJEb3Sn","reason":"tool-calls","snapshot":"f33c5114db06c230ebdbad281b75532a26b6f114","messageID":"msg_d781b3179001BVG1C6JVlSFB5C","sessionID":"ses_287e60928ffeqArVIHjn8RDz06","type":"step-finish","tokens":{"total":28219,"input":28044,"output":148,"reasoning":27,"cache":{"write":0,"read":0}},"cost":0.008029069}}
{"type":"step_start","timestamp":1775836549167,"sessionID":"ses_287e60928ffeqArVIHjn8RDz06","part":{"id":"prt_d781b502c0016Tig0lGh6HEJ9s","messageID":"msg_d781b4275001JQ9Ln8lCGJ47OF","sessionID":"ses_287e60928ffeqArVIHjn8RDz06","snapshot":"f33c5114db06c230ebdbad281b75532a26b6f114","type":"step-start"}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775836639046,"sessionID":"ses_287e60928ffeqArVIHjn8RDz06","part":{"id":"prt_d781b7837001eTGhn2GfYoidoo","messageID":"msg_d781b4275001JQ9Ln8lCGJ47OF","sessionID":"ses_287e60928ffeqArVIHjn8RDz06","type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"call_b7dd69dc07e64461985f0753","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"content":"# AR-014: Valkey 存储实现 — Delta Spec\n\n## Context\n\n- **Module:** `pkg/store`\n- **Language:** Go\n- **Size:** S\n- **Base specs:** `session-store/spec.md`, `session-store/design.md`, `deployment/client-go.md`\n\n## Delta Requirements\n\n### Requirement: Valkey client initialization\nThe Valkey implementation SHALL construct a `valkey.Client` using `github.com/valkey-io/valkey-go`. The system SHALL require `VALKEY_ADDR` to be non-empty (comma-separated list split into `InitAddress`). The system SHALL require non-empty `VALKEY_PASSWORD` unless `VALKEY_PASSWORD_REQUIRED` is set case-insensitively to `\"false\"`.\n\n#### Scenario: Successful initialization with address and password\n- **GIVEN** `VALKEY_ADDR` is set to `\"localhost:6379\"` and `VALKEY_PASSWORD` is set to `\"secret\"`\n- **WHEN** the Valkey store initializes\n- **THEN** a `valkey.Client` is constructed with `InitAddress: []string{\"localhost:6379\"}` and `Password: \"secret\"`\n- **AND** no error is returned\n\n#### Scenario: Comma-separated addresses\n- **GIVEN** `VALKEY_ADDR` is set to `\"host1:6379,host2:6379\"`\n- **WHEN** the Valkey store initializes\n- **THEN** `InitAddress` is `[]string{\"host1:6379\", \"host2:6379\"}`\n\n#### Scenario: Missing address fails\n- **GIVEN** `VALKEY_ADDR` is empty or unset\n- **WHEN** the Valkey store initializes\n- **THEN** initialization returns an error indicating `VALKEY_ADDR` is required\n\n#### Scenario: Password required by default\n- **GIVEN** `VALKEY_ADDR` is set, `VALKEY_PASSWORD` is empty, and `VALKEY_PASSWORD_REQUIRED` is unset\n- **WHEN** the Valkey store initializes\n- **THEN** initialization fails with an error stating password is required\n\n#### Scenario: Password bypass when explicitly disabled\n- **GIVEN** `VALKEY_ADDR` is set, `VALKEY_PASSWORD` is empty, and `VALKEY_PASSWORD_REQUIRED` is set to `\"false\"` (case-insensitive)\n- **WHEN** the Valkey store initializes\n- **THEN** a `valkey.Client` is constructed with empty password\n- **AND** no error is returned\n\n### Requirement: Valkey connection options\nThe system SHALL build `valkey.ClientOption` with `InitAddress` from splitting `VALKEY_ADDR` by comma and `Password` from `VALKEY_PASSWORD`. Optional flags `DisableCache` and `ForceSingleClient` SHALL be set when their respective environment variables parse as true via `strconv.ParseBool`.\n\n#### Scenario: Options construction with defaults\n- **GIVEN** `VALKEY_ADDR=\"valkey-host:6380\"` and `VALKEY_PASSWORD=\"pass123\"`\n- **WHEN** `makeValkeyOptions()` is called\n- **THEN** the returned `ClientOption` has `InitAddress: []string{\"valkey-host:6380\"}` and `Password: \"pass123\"`\n- **AND** `DisableCache` and `ForceSingleClient` are `false`\n\n#### Scenario: DisableCache enabled\n- **GIVEN** `VALKEY_DISABLE_CACHE=true`\n- **WHEN** Valkey client options are built\n- **THEN** `DisableCache` is `true` on `ClientOption`\n\n#### Scenario: ForceSingleClient enabled\n- **GIVEN** `VALKEY_FORCE_SINGLE=true`\n- **WHEN** Valkey client options are built\n- **THEN** `ForceSingleClient` is `true` on `ClientOption`\n\n#### Scenario: Invalid bool value ignored\n- **GIVEN** `VALKEY_DISABLE_CACHE=invalid`\n- **WHEN** Valkey client options are built\n- **THEN** `DisableCache` remains `false` (ParseBool error, flag not set)\n\n### Requirement: Valkey StoreSandbox multi-command execution\nThe Valkey implementation SHALL execute `StoreSandbox` via `DoMulti` with three commands: `SETNX` on the session key with JSON value, `ZADD` on `session:expiry` with score = `float64(ExpiresAt.Unix())`, and `ZADD` on `session:last_activity` with score = `float64(time.Now().Unix())`. The system SHALL fail if any command in the batch returns an error.\n\n#### Scenario: Successful store multi\n- **GIVEN** a valid `SandboxInfo` with non-zero `ExpiresAt` and session id `s1`\n- **WHEN** `StoreSandbox(ctx, sandbox)` is called on the Valkey store\n- **THEN** `DoMulti` executes `SETNX session:s1 <json>`, `ZADD session:expiry <expires_unix> s1`, `ZADD session:last_activity <now_unix> s1` and returns nil\n\n#### Scenario: Multi error propagation\n- **GIVEN** the Valkey server is unreachable during `StoreSandbox`\n- **WHEN** `DoMulti` executes\n- **THEN** the method returns a non-nil error and no partial state is committed\n\n#### Scenario: Nil sandbox rejected\n- **GIVEN** `StoreSandbox(ctx, nil)` is called\n- **WHEN** the method executes\n- **THEN** an error is returned indicating sandbox is nil\n- **AND** no Valkey commands are issued\n\n#### Scenario: Zero ExpiresAt rejected\n- **GIVEN** `SandboxInfo` has `ExpiresAt == time.Time{}`\n- **WHEN** `StoreSandbox(ctx, sandbox)` is called\n- **THEN** an error is returned indicating ExpiresAt is required\n- **AND** no Valkey commands are issued\n\n### Requirement: Valkey UpdateSandbox XX semantics\nThe Valkey implementation SHALL use `SET key value XX` for `UpdateSandbox`. If the key does not exist, the response will not be `\"OK\"` and the system SHALL return an error indicating the key does not exist.\n\n#### Scenario: Update existing key\n- **GIVEN** session key `session:s1` exists\n- **WHEN** `UpdateSandbox(ctx, sandbox)` is called\n- **THEN** the JSON value is overwritten, response is `\"OK\"`, and the method returns nil\n\n#### Scenario: Update missing key\n- **GIVEN** session key `session:s1` does not exist\n- **WHEN** `UpdateSandbox(ctx, sandbox)` is called\n- **THEN** the method returns an error containing `key not exists`\n\n#### Scenario: Nil sandbox rejected on update\n- **GIVEN** `UpdateSandbox(ctx, nil)` is called\n- **WHEN** the method executes\n- **THEN** an error is returned indicating sandbox is nil\n\n### Requirement: Valkey DeleteSandboxBySessionID multi-command execution\nThe Valkey implementation SHALL execute `DeleteSandboxBySessionID` via `DoMulti` with three commands: `DEL` on the session key, `ZREM` on `session:expiry`, and `ZREM` on `session:last_activity`.\n\n#### Scenario: Full deletion\n- **GIVEN** session `s1` exists with entries in both ZSETs\n- **WHEN** `DeleteSandboxBySessionID(ctx, \"s1\")` succeeds\n- **THEN** `GET session:s1` returns not found and both ZSETs no longer contain member `s1`\n\n#### Scenario: Delete non-existent session\n- **GIVEN** session `ghost` does not exist\n- **WHEN** `DeleteSandboxBySessionID(ctx, \"ghost\")` is called\n- **THEN** `DoMulti` executes (DEL returns 0, ZREM returns 0) and no error is returned\n\n### Requirement: Valkey GetSandboxBySessionID\nThe Valkey implementation SHALL retrieve a sandbox document using `B().Get().Key(key)`. If the key does not exist (`IsValkeyNil` returns true), the system SHALL return `ErrNotFound`.\n\n#### Scenario: Existing session retrieved\n- **GIVEN** a sandbox document exists at key `session:s1`\n- **WHEN** `GetSandboxBySessionID(ctx, \"s1\")` is called\n- **THEN** the bytes are unmarshaled to `*types.SandboxInfo` and returned with nil error\n\n#### Scenario: Missing session returns ErrNotFound\n- **GIVEN** no key exists at `session:missing`\n- **WHEN** `GetSandboxBySessionID(ctx, \"missing\")` is called\n- **THEN** `IsValkeyNil` is true and the method returns `ErrNotFound`\n\n### Requirement: Valkey ListExpiredSandboxes query\nThe Valkey implementation SHALL query `session:expiry` using `Zrangebyscore` with `Min(\"-inf\")`, `Max(fmt.Sprintf(\"%d\", before.Unix()))`, and `Limit(0, limit)`. When `limit <= 0`, the method SHALL return `nil, nil`.\n\n#### Scenario: List with limit zero\n- **GIVEN** expired sessions exist in the index\n- **WHEN** `ListExpiredSandboxes(ctx, before, 0)` is called\n- **THEN** the method returns `nil, nil` without querying Valkey\n\n#### Scenario: List with positive limit\n- **GIVEN** three sessions have expiry scores ≤ `before.Unix()`\n- **WHEN** `ListExpiredSandboxes(ctx, before, 2)` is called\n- **THEN** at most two `SandboxInfo` pointers are returned\n\n#### Scenario: List with negative limit\n- **GIVEN** expired sessions exist\n- **WHEN** `ListExpiredSandboxes(ctx, before, -1)` is called\n- **THEN** the method returns `nil, nil`\n\n### Requirement: Valkey ListInactiveSandboxes query\nThe Valkey implementation SHALL query `session:last_activity` using `Zrangebyscore` with the same score range pattern as `ListExpiredSandboxes`. When `limit <= 0`, the method SHALL return `nil, nil`.\n\n#### Scenario: Inactive list with negative limit\n- **GIVEN** inactive sessions exist\n- **WHEN** `ListInactiveSandboxes(ctx, before, -1)` is called\n- **THEN** the method returns `nil, nil`\n\n#### Scenario: Inactive list with positive limit\n- **GIVEN** two sessions have last-activity scores ≤ `before.Unix()`\n- **WHEN** `ListInactiveSandboxes(ctx, before, 5)` is called\n- **THEN** up to two `SandboxInfo` pointers are returned\n\n### Requirement: Valkey UpdateSessionLastActivity precondition\nThe Valkey implementation SHALL reject empty session id. If `at` is zero time, the system SHALL use `time.Now()`. The system SHALL verify the session key exists via `B().Exists().Key(key)` (result must be 1). If the key is absent, the method SHALL return `ErrNotFound`. Then `ZADD` the session id to `session:last_activity` with the activity score.\n\n#### Scenario: Activity update with zero time\n- **GIVEN** session `s1` exists and `at` is `time.Time{}`\n- **WHEN** `UpdateSessionLastActivity(ctx, \"s1\", at)` is called\n- **THEN** `ZADD session:last_activity <now_unix> s1` is executed\n\n#### Scenario: Activity update for missing session\n- **GIVEN** session `s1` does not exist\n- **WHEN** `UpdateSessionLastActivity(ctx, \"s1\", now)` is called\n- **THEN** `Exists` returns 0 and the method returns `ErrNotFound`\n\n#### Scenario: Empty session ID rejected\n- **GIVEN** empty session ID `\"\"`\n- **WHEN** `UpdateSessionLastActivity(ctx, \"\", at)` is called\n- **THEN** an error is returned indicating session ID is empty\n\n### Requirement: Valkey MGET orphan tolerance\nThe Valkey implementation SHALL handle empty string results from `Mget` commands when loading sandboxes by session IDs via `loadSandboxesBySessionIDs`. Entries with empty string results SHALL be skipped without failing the batch.\n\n#### Scenario: Valkey orphan ZSET member\n- **GIVEN** session id `ghost` is in `session:last_activity` but `session:ghost` does not exist\n- **WHEN** `ListInactiveSandboxes` loads the batch via `Mget`\n- **THEN** `ghost` is omitted from the result slice\n- **AND** no error is raised\n\n#### Scenario: All keys present in MGET\n- **GIVEN** session ids `[\"a\", \"b\"]` both have corresponding keys with valid JSON\n- **WHEN** `loadSandboxesBySessionIDs(ctx, [\"a\", \"b\"])` is called\n- **THEN** `Mget` returns both values and both are unmarshaled into the result slice\n\n#### Scenario: Mixed present and missing keys\n- **GIVEN** session id `a` has a key but `b` does not\n- **WHEN** `loadSandboxesBySessionIDs(ctx, [\"a\", \"b\"])` is called\n- **THEN** `b`'s empty result is skipped and only `a`'s `SandboxInfo` is returned\n\n### Requirement: Valkey Ping response validation\nThe Valkey implementation SHALL issue `PING` via `B().Ping()` and validate the string response equals `PONG`.\n\n#### Scenario: Healthy Valkey\n- **GIVEN** Valkey server is running\n- **WHEN** `Ping(ctx)` is called\n- **THEN** the response is `PONG` and nil error is returned\n\n#### Scenario: Unreachable Valkey\n- **GIVEN** Valkey server is down\n- **WHEN** `Ping(ctx)` is called\n- **THEN** an error is returned indicating connection failure\n\n### Requirement: Valkey Close operation\nThe Valkey implementation SHALL close the client connection via `vs.cli.Close()` and return nil.\n\n#### Scenario: Client closed successfully\n- **GIVEN** an active Valkey store\n- **WHEN** `Close()` is called\n- **THEN** `vs.cli.Close()` is invoked and nil is returned\n\n### Requirement: Valkey fixed key patterns\nThe Valkey implementation SHALL use the following fixed key patterns: `sessionPrefix = \"session:\"`, `expiryIndexKey = \"session:expiry\"`, `lastActivityIndexKey = \"session:last_activity\"`.\n\n#### Scenario: Session key construction\n- **GIVEN** session id `abc`\n- **WHEN** the store constructs the key\n- **THEN** the key is `session:abc`\n\n### Requirement: Valkey ZSET score semantics\nThe system SHALL use Unix seconds as scores in sorted sets. Expiry index score = `float64(ExpiresAt.Unix())` on store. Last activity score = `float64(time.Now().Unix())` on `StoreSandbox`, `float64(at.Unix())` on `UpdateSessionLastActivity`.\n\n#### Scenario: Expiry score is sandbox ExpiresAt\n- **GIVEN** a sandbox with `ExpiresAt` set to a specific time T\n- **WHEN** `StoreSandbox` adds to `session:expiry`\n- **THEN** the score is `float64(T.Unix())`\n\n#### Scenario: Last activity score is current time on store\n- **GIVEN** `StoreSandbox` is called at time T\n- **WHEN** the sandbox is added to `session:last_activity`\n- **THEN** the score is `float64(T.Unix())`\n\n#### Scenario: Last activity score uses provided time on update\n- **GIVEN** `UpdateSessionLastActivity` is called with time T\n- **WHEN** the ZADD is executed on `session:last_activity`\n- **THEN** the score is `float64(T.Unix())`\n\n### Requirement: Provider selection via STORE_TYPE for Valkey\nWhen `STORE_TYPE` is set case-insensitively to `\"valkey\"`, the system SHALL construct the Valkey implementation.\n\n#### Scenario: Valkey selected\n- **GIVEN** `STORE_TYPE` is set to `\"valkey\"`\n- **WHEN** `Storage()` initializes\n- **THEN** the Valkey implementation is constructed\n\n#### Scenario: Case-insensitive valkey match\n- **GIVEN** `STORE_TYPE` is set to `\"VALKEY\"`\n- **WHEN** `Storage()` initializes\n- **THEN** the Valkey implementation is constructed\n\n### Requirement: Valkey struct definition\nThe Valkey implementation SHALL define a `valkeyStore` struct with fields: `cli valkey.Client`, `sessionPrefix string`, `expiryIndexKey string`, `lastActivityIndexKey string`.\n\n#### Scenario: Struct field initialization\n- **GIVEN** a new `valkeyStore` is constructed\n- **WHEN** fields are inspected\n- **THEN** `sessionPrefix` is `\"session:\"`, `expiryIndexKey` is `\"session:expiry\"`, `lastActivityIndexKey` is `\"session:last_activity\"`\n","filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/delta-spec.md"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.","metadata":{"diagnostics":{},"filepath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/delta-spec.md","exists":true,"truncated":false},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/delta-spec.md","time":{"start":1775836639020,"end":1775836639044}}}}
