{"type":"text","timestamp":1775836648364,"sessionID":"ses_287e60928ffeqArVIHjn8RDz06","part":{"id":"prt_d781cc2bd001OyjX6DbcYYrsBk","messageID":"msg_d781cafba0019oF6q555puwqc8","sessionID":"ses_287e60928ffeqArVIHjn8RDz06","type":"text","text":"Written `delta-spec.md` for AR-014 — Valkey 存储实现 with 28 requirements and their acceptance scenarios covering:\n\n- **Client initialization**: address parsing, password policy, optional flags (`DisableCache`, `ForceSingleClient`)\n- **Store operations**: `StoreSandbox` via `DoMulti`, `UpdateSandbox` XX semantics, `DeleteSandboxBySessionID`\n- **Read operations**: `GetSandboxBySessionID` with `IsValkeyNil` → `ErrNotFound`\n- **List operations**: `ListExpiredSandboxes` / `ListInactiveSandboxes` via `Zrangebyscore`, `loadSandboxesBySessionIDs` via `Mget` with orphan tolerance\n- **Activity tracking**: `UpdateSessionLastActivity` with `Exists` precondition\n- **Connection**: `Ping` via `B().Ping()`, `Close`\n- **Provider selection**: `STORE_TYPE=valkey` case-insensitive matching\n- **Struct/key patterns**: `valkeyStore` fields, fixed key constants, ZSET score semantics","time":{"start":1775836648362,"end":1775836648362}}}
